### B. Financial Column Authority

| Column | Source of Truth | Update Frequency |
|--------|----------------|-----------------|
| `reservations.total_amount` | Streamline `GetReservationPrice` | Per-sync (5 min) |
| `reservations.cleaning_fee` | Extracted from `required_fees[]` | Per-enrichment |
| `reservations.damage_waiver_fee` | Extracted from `required_fees[]` | Per-enrichment |
| `reservations.tax_amount` | Streamline `taxes` field | Per-enrichment |
| `properties.owner_balance` | Streamline `GetUnitOwnerBalance` | Per-sync |
